      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "(Please note that the full Hadeeth is to be found in Al Kafi – V 4 – The Book of Hajj Ch 28 H 37, for the answer to the second man)",
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Ablution <span class=\"iTxt\">(Wudhu)</span> is part of the <span class=\"iTxt\">Emaan</span> (faith)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from al-Nawfaliy from al-Sakuniy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Wudu’ is part of belief.’” "
        ]
      }
